    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer273310973" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11167055591538376281">The ultimate book on that deeply flawed operation with Paratroopers that failed at the bridge at Arnhem. ANd as a consequense the Northern part of the Netherlands remained in German hands for another winter (the Hungerwinter).<br/><br/>About the brave men and women that lived through this chapter of WOII that is still remembered today.<br/><br/>The writing is a bit dry but the story is well told. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


