<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/716532.The_Day_of_Battle"><img alt="The Day of Battle: The War in Sicily and Italy, 1943-1944 (World War II Liberation Trilogy, #2)" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1442525486l/716532._SX98_.jpg" />
